%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
flowchart TD
    Query[Authenticated Query] --> Context[Extract Tenant + User + ABAC]
    Context --> Authz[RBAC + ABAC + Consent Check]
    Authz -->|Denied| Deny[403 Forbidden + Audit]
    
    Authz -->|Allowed| Filters[Build Metadata Filters<br/>tenant, patient, dept, date, sensitivity]
    Filters --> Embed[Embed Query]
    Embed --> Hybrid[Hybrid Search<br/>Vector + Keyword + Filters]
    Hybrid --> Rerank[Reranking + Dedup]
    Rerank --> MCP[MCP Governance Layer]
    MCP --> LLM[Grounded LLM Generation<br/>+ Citations + Disclaimers]
    LLM --> Audit[Full Audit Record]
    LLM --> Response[Safe Response to User]
